#: ../../library/locale.rst:353 ../../library/locale.rst:368
msgid ""
"The language code has the same format as a :ref:`locale name <locale_name>`, "
"but without encoding and ``@``-modifier. The language code and encoding may "
"be ``None`` if their values cannot be determined. The \"C\" locale is "
"represented as ``(None, None)``."
